              "blocks": {}
            },
            "about_heading": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Bacii celebrates the big personalities packed into little people.</p>",
                "width": "fill",
                "max_width": "normal",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "h2",
                "font": "var(--font-heading--family)",
                "font_size": "",
                "line_height": "normal",
                "letter_spacing": "normal",
                "case": "none",
                "wrap": "pretty",
                "text_color": "#FCF5EF",
                "background": false,
                "background_color": "#00000026",
                "corner_radius": 0,
                "padding-block-start": 0,
                "padding-block-end": 0,
                "padding-inline-start": 0,
                "padding-inline-end": 0
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "about_body": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Bacii was born from the beautiful chaos of childhood. Created by a mum of two boys, Bacii began with a simple idea: children's clothing should feel as playful, expressive and unique as the little people wearing it. When I couldn't find pieces that felt fun without being over the top, and elevated without losing personality, I decided to create them. Designed in Australia and made from premium organic cotton, Bacii combines playful graphics, thoughtful colours and relaxed silhouettes made for everyday adventures — from playgrounds and park dates to snack breaks and sofa cuddles.</p>",
